# This directory is used for intermediate files during catchment delineation
# Files generated here:
# - surface_dem.tif (DEM exported from Civil 3D)
# - inlet_structures.shp (Pour points from pipe network)
# - dem_conditioned.tif (Depression-removed DEM)
# - flow_direction.tif (D8 flow direction)
# - flow_accumulation.tif (Contributing area)
# - pour_points_snapped.shp (Snapped inlet locations)
# - watersheds.tif (Watershed raster)
# - catchments.shp (Final output polygons)

